<div class="nbunit" id="a30Dec1938"><font color="red">30 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  Many thanks for your letter &hellip; of 28th December and for the corrected pages 257-355 revised for press, provided Mr de la Mare thinks the red ink instructions are clear. </div>
